column5: I am taking a trip up to the red and winnepeg rivers sept 14-20.I am going up there basically blind as to where to go, lures, etc. I would appreciate any and all insights about this place and how to have some fun catching some walleyes. All I know at this point is I have a reservation at a little place in Selkirk.Thanks in advance for anything you have to tell me
Stay in Pine Falls when fishing the Winnipeg river is close to boat launch night life ect.
